Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:08.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}旅の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:13.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}心だけ 彷徨って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:17.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}立ち尽くした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:21.49,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}でも今は 遠くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:25.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:30.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}そうキミと この道で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}出会ってから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:42.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}旅人達が歌う 見知らぬ歌も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:47.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}懐かしく聞こえてくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:52.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}ただキミといると
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:57.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}夢見た世界が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:01.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}どこかにあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:05.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}探しに行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}風の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:13.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}凍て付く夜明けの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:18.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}乾いた真昼の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:22.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}震える闇夜の
